<p begin="00:00:02.569" end="00:00:03.971" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; Stephen:  WELCOME BACK, </span><span style="block">EVERYBODY.</span></p>

<p begin="00:00:03.971" end="00:00:15.349" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">MY GUEST TONIGHT IS AN </span><span style="block">OSCAR-WINNING ACTOR WHO PLAYS </span><span style="block">THE MANDARIN IN "IRON MAN 3".</span></p>


<p begin="00:00:15.349" end="00:00:22.289" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; MR. PRESIDENT, ONLY TWO </span><span style="block">LESSONS REMAIN.</span></p>

<p begin="00:00:22.289" end="00:00:24.858" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">I INTEND TO FINISH THIS BEFORE </span><span style="block">CHRISTMAS MORNING.</span></p>

