<p begin="00:00:28.929" end="00:00:38.639" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">THOMAS HERE IS AN ACCOUNTANT FOR </span><span style="block">THE ROXON OIL CORPORATION, AND </span><span style="block">I'M SURE HE'S A REALLY GOOD GUY.</span></p>


<p begin="00:00:38.639" end="00:00:40.941" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">I'M GOING TO SHOOT HIM IN THE </span><span style="block">HEAD.</span></p>

