<p begin="00:00:44.378" end="00:00:47.714" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; Stephen:  NOT IF OBAMA </span><span style="block">TAKES HIS GUN AWAY.</span></p>

<p begin="00:00:47.714" end="00:00:51.885" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">( LAUGHTER ) </span><span style="block">PLEASE WELCOME SIR BEN KINGSLEY.</span></p>

