<p begin="00:00:58.892" end="00:01:00.227" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">NICE TO MEET YOU.</span></p>
<p begin="00:01:00.227" end="00:01:01.328" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">THANKS SO MUCH FOR COMING.</span></p>
